{"tid":1074864,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺俾料你要自己煮嘅餐廳好呃錢？","createTime":"2019-03-23T16:49:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-24T10:57:59.000Z","uid":60171,"like":31,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4210e3acdfd03738c76b29754445e9b231c6fb93","tid":1074864,"uid":60171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T16:49:24.000Z","msg":"唔知幾時開始香港就有堆懶係搞新意嘅餐廳入侵香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩吉列牛呀大阪燒呀俾塊扒你自己煎嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />諸如此類<br />\n俾個食材你跟住自由發揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住煮岀嚟唔好食餐廳係完全無責任，因為係你自己整得唔好，煮太耐又得煮得太短時間<br />\n煮燶左唔靚又無得打卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自己又要食癌細胞落肚，洗嗰個又麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一啲明明可以廚房搞掂嘅野依家順理成章交俾個客搞屎棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本係揾笨呃錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要自己整咁不如我返屋企煮算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n岀街食原意就係唔洗咁麻煩翹埋手就有得食嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞場大龍鳳身水身汗做咩姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ecb8b2a54a675b8734e69c08f9f6ec737524cc0","tid":1074864,"uid":143582,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T16:50:38.000Z","msg":"咁講打邊爐 bbq都係.."},{"pid":"fae6fd7ccc1ccffc85ed90009a407025ee2d3ed8","tid":1074864,"uid":60735,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T16:50:42.000Z","msg":"有人受落就得。"},{"pid":"292803db4044784cc8f9b05cdf7e014797f26283","tid":1074864,"uid":60171,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3ecb8b2a54a675b8734e69c08f9f6ec737524cc0","tid":1074864,"uid":143582,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T16:50:38.000Z","msg":"咁講打邊爐 bbq都係.."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T16:52:04.000Z","msg":"打邊爐 bbq你有得揀任食<br />\n我講嗰啲會唔會有？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8d00eef53e2227998e2774d768eb56fff31233","tid":1074864,"uid":77832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T16:52:16.000Z","msg":"咁你唔自己煮? 咁撚多野講 你咪又係出去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c95dd4bf0f99dadf99aa08d750556ead9b04d1ec","tid":1074864,"uid":60171,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"db8d00eef53e2227998e2774d768eb56fff31233","tid":1074864,"uid":77832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T16:52:16.000Z","msg":"咁你唔自己煮? 咁撚多野講 你咪又係出去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T16:53:52.000Z","msg":"會岀去食，但唔會幫襯呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行過望到都覺得毫無興趣"},{"pid":"280b3b9e63be2f67e69de7506c8aebba2e232073","tid":1074864,"uid":106326,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T18:18:50.000Z","msg":"大阪燒都ok 低技術 唔洗點理佢<br />\n當玩下 但本身係日本係平野黎 黎到香港就變貴<br />\n算數 當飛機貴<br />\n但食肉個啲真係咪撚搞<br />\n鐵板燒就係貪睇住個師傅係你面前煮<br />\n而且手藝好既話 連炒野菜都可以炒到好好食"},{"pid":"95cdca9d45772caf3605a7d9eb44cf08dd1f64cf","tid":1074864,"uid":60171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"280b3b9e63be2f67e69de7506c8aebba2e232073","tid":1074864,"uid":106326,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T18:18:50.000Z","msg":"大阪燒都ok 低技術 唔洗點理佢<br />\n當玩下 但本身係日本係平野黎 黎到香港就變貴<br />\n算數 當飛機貴<br />\n但食肉個啲真係咪撚搞<br />\n鐵板燒就係貪睇住個師傅係你面前煮<br />\n而且手藝好既話 連炒野菜都可以炒到好好食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T01:48:03.000Z","msg":"認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"